CustomField.description:
This is the columns for Activity Table in JSON format e.g

{"fieldName":"Id", "label": "Subject", "type": "url",
"typeAttributes": {
"label": {
"fieldName": "Subject"
}
}},
{"fieldName" : "CreatedDate", "label" : "Created Date", "type": "date-local", "typeAttributes":{
"month": "2-digit",
"day": "2-digit"
}},
{"fieldName" : "CreatedBy.Name", "label" : "Created By"},
